my bruschetta pasta salad\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e too – just knock out all the chopping of the tomatoes and garlic in one night! You can also serve it alongside some \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2018/08/best-grilled-vegetables/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003egrilled vegetables\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e or my \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/02/baked-cheesy-rice/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ebaked cheesy rice\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e. \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eOr \u003c/span\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2024/03/roasted-asparagus/\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eroasted asparagus with lemon\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cspan\u003e! The crisp, springy spears are only made better served with it. \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan id=\"more-99067\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-6-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"bruschetta salmon\" width=\"1773\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Bruschetta Balsamic Salmon.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-6-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-6-scaled.jpg 1773w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-6-728x903.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-6-768x953.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-6-1238x1536.jpg 1238w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-6-1651x2048.jpg 1651w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-6-150x186.jpg 150w\