weeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-10-96x96.jpg 96w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%20200%20200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-10-250x250.jpg 250w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-10-500x500.jpg 500w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-10-336x336.jpg 336w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-10-672x672.jpg 672w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-10-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-10-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-10-96x96.jpg 96w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-10-250x250.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2\u003eBruschetta Balsamic Salmon\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" x=\"0px\" y=\"0px\" width=\"16px\" height=\"16px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"\u003e\u003cg\u003e\u003cpath fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M10,0C9.4,0,9,0.4,9,1v4H7V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S5,0.4,5,1v4H3V1c0-0.6-0.4-1-1-1S1,0.4,1,1v8c0,1.7,1.3,3,3,3v10c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V12c1.7,0,3-1.3,3-3V1C11,0.4,10.6,0,10,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003cpath data-color=\"color-2\" fill=\"#ae0481\" d=\"M19,0c-3.3,0-6,2.7-6,6v9c0,0.6,0.4,1,1,1h2v6c0,1.1,0.9,2,2,2s2-0.9,2-2V1C20,0.4,19.6,0,19,0z\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/g\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eYield: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan data-recipe=\"99081\" aria-label=\"Adjust recipe servings\"\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePrep Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCook Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e10\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eTotal Time: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003cspan\u003e20\u003cspan\u003e minutes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\t\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis bruschetta salmon is an easy and versatile weeknight meal. Seared salmon drizzled with syrupy balsamic glaze and topped with diced tomatoes, garlic and fresh basil tastes like summer. Serve with your favorite side dish for a simple dinner!\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"99081\" data-servings=\"4\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"0\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1 ½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecups\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ehalved cherry or grape tomatoes\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"1\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003ecup\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eof chiffonade fresh basil\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"2\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/spice-world-fresh-whole-garlic-3ct-bag/-/A-14917318?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic cloves,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eminced\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"3\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ekosher salt and pepper\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"4\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1 ½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003etablespoons\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/pure-olive-oil-25-5oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77600361?aflt=plt#lnk=sametab\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eolive oil\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"5\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e4\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003esalmon filets\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"6\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e1\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/garlic-powder-3-12oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77585075?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003egarlic powder\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"7\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e½\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003eteaspoon\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.target.com/p/ground-italian-seasoning-0-75oz-good-38-gather-8482/-/A-77587153?aflt=plt\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003eitalian seasoning\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli data-uid=\"8\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://amzn.to/3SpQyGK\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"\u003ebalsamic glaze,\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e \u003cspan\u003efor drizzling\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv data-recipe=\"99081\"\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99081-step-0-0\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn a bowl, stir together the tomatoes, basil, garlic and a big pinch of salt and pepper. Add ½ tablespoon of olive oil and toss well. Set aside.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99081-step-0-1\"\u003e\u003cp\u003ePat the salmon dry with paper towels. Season the salmon all over with the salt, pepper, italian seasoning and garlic powder.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99081-step-0-2\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eHeat the remaining 1 tablespoon olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat. Once hot, add the salmon in a single layer. Cook until golden on the bottom, about 2 to 3 minutes. Gently flip and cook until it’s golden brown on the other side and cooked through. It will easily flake with a fork.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli id=\"wprm-recipe-99081-step-0-3\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eOnce the salmon is cooked through, drizzle the balsamic glaze on top. Remove from the pan. Top the salmon with the bruschetta mixture and serve immediately.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCourse: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eMain Course\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eCuisine: \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003eAmerican\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-12-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"bruschetta salmon\" width=\"1847\" height=\"2200\" data-jpibfi-post-excerpt=\"\" data-jpibfi-post-url=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon/\" data-jpibfi-post-title=\"Bruschetta Balsamic Salmon.\" data-jpibfi-src=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-12-scaled.jpg\" srcset=\"https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-12-scaled.jpg 1847w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-12-728x867.jpg 728w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-12-768x915.jpg 768w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-12-1289x1536.jpg 1289w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-12-1719x2048.jpg 1719w, https://www.howsweeteats.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/bruschetta-salmon-12-150x179.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1847px) 100vw, 1847px\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe garlic bread and soak up all that goodness too.\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\n\t\t\n\u003c/article\u003e \n\n\t\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\t\n\n\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
